g kh\u00e1ch c\u0103n h\u1ed9 cao c\u1ea5p c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 sang tr\u1ecdng<\/em><\/p>\n<p>S\u1ef1 uy\u1ec3n chuy\u1ec3n trong t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7, \u0111i\u1ec3m xuy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>N\u1ed9i dung ch&iacute;nh1 5 qui t\u1eafc khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t chung c\u01b0 cao c\u1ea5p1.1 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a01. H\u00e3y ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 phong th\u1ee7y:1.2 \u00a0 \u00a02. C\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7: Trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t n\u00f3i chung, hay\u00a0thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t chung c\u01b0 cao c\u1ea5p\u00a0n\u00f3i ri\u00eang, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":23,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[3],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/noithat5nbs.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/149"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/noithat5nbs.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/noithat5nbs.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/noithat5nbs.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/noithat5nbs.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=149"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/noithat5nbs.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/149\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/noithat5nbs.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/noithat5nbs.webs